<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV43">
<l>veñciṉatta vēḻaveṇma ruppocittu ruttamā</l>
<l>kañcaṉaikka ṭintumaṇṇa ḷantukoṇṭa kālaṉē</l>
<l>vañcaṉattu vantapēycci yāvipāluḷ vāṅkiṉā</l>
<l>yañcaṉatta vaṇṇaṉāya vātitēva ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O death who measured for Yourself the earth, having destroyed</l>
<l>The strong, angry Kaṃsa, after breaking the white tusks of the mightily angry elephants!</l>
<l>O You who extracted the life-breath of the demoness who had come with the milk out</l>
<l rend="indent">of deceit!</l>
<l>Aren’t You the Primary Lord of the hue of collyrium?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
